SELECT g.DESCR , g.CRSE_GRADE_INPUT , %Round(g.GRADE_POINTS, 3) , g.GRADING_BASIS , g.VALID_ATTEMPT , g.EARN_CREDIT , g.INCLUDE_IN_GPA FROM %Table(GRADE_TBL) g WHERE g.SETID = :1 AND g.EFFDT = ( SELECT MAX(G_ED.EFFDT) FROM %Table(GRADE_TBL) G_ED WHERE G_ED.SETID = G.SETID AND G_ED.GRADING_SCHEME = G.GRADING_SCHEME AND G_ED.EFFDT <= %CurrentDateTimeIn)

POINTER
GBL 32
1900-01-01 CCTC Academic Summary Get 974 POINTER
SELECT A.EMPLID , A.TOT_TAKEN_GPA , A.TOT_PASSD_GPA , A.TOT_GRADE_POINTS , CASE WHEN A.CUM_GPA = 0 THEN 0 ELSE %Round(A.TOT_GRADE_POINTS/A.CUM_GPA, 1) END , A.CUM_GPA , A.ACAD_LEVEL_EOT FROM %Table(STDNT_CAR_TERM) A WHERE A.EMPLID = :1 AND A.INSTITUTION = :2 AND A.ACAD_CAREER = :3 AND A.STRM = ( SELECT MAX(A_ED.STRM) FROM %Table(STDNT_CAR_TERM) A_ED WHERE A_ED.EMPLID = A.EMPLID AND A_ED.INSTITUTION = A.INSTITUTION AND A_ED.ACAD_CAREER = A.ACAD_CAREER)
270 POINTER
California Community Colleges Tech Center: Retrieves the given Student's Overall Academic Summary across all terms in the given career.
0 HANDLE

POINTER
GBL 32
1900-01-01 CCTC Student Coursework Get 2742 POINTER
SELECT A.EMPLID , A.STRM , C.CIP_CODE , B.SUBJECT , B.CATALOG_NBR , B.DESCR , A.ENRL_ADD_DT , A.ENRL_DROP_DT , A.CRSE_GRADE_OFF , A.GRADING_BASIS_ENRL , A.UNT_TAKEN , A.UNT_EARNED , A.GRADE_POINTS , A.INCLUDE_IN_GPA , A.REPEAT_CODE , N.DESCR FROM %Table(STDNT_ENRL) A JOIN %Table(CLASS_TBL) B ON (A.INSTITUTION = B.INSTITUTION AND A.ACAD_CAREER = B.ACAD_CAREER AND A.STRM = B.STRM AND A.CLASS_NBR = B.CLASS_NBR) JOIN %Table(SESSION_TBL) S ON (A.INSTITUTION = S.INSTITUTION AND A.ACAD_CAREER = S.ACAD_CAREER AND A.STRM = S.STRM AND A.SESSION_CODE = S.SESSION_CODE) JOIN %Table(CRSE_OFFER) C ON (B.INSTITUTION = C.INSTITUTION AND B.CRSE_ID = C.CRSE_ID AND B.CRSE_OFFER_NBR = C.CRSE_OFFER_NBR) LEFT OUTER JOIN ( SELECT N1.TSCRPT_NOTE_ID , N1.DESCR FROM %Table(TSCRPT_NOTE_TBL) N1 WHERE N1.EFFDT = ( SELECT MAX(N1_ED.EFFDT) FROM %Table(TSCRPT_NOTE_TBL) N1_ED WHERE N1_ED.SETID = N1.SETID AND N1_ED.TSCRPT_NOTE_ID = N1.TSCRPT_NOTE_ID) AND N1.EFF_STATUS = 'A') N ON (A.TSCRPT_NOTE_ID = N.TSCRPT_NOTE_ID) WHERE A.EMPLID = :1 AND A.INSTITUTION = :2 AND A.ACAD_CAREER = :3 AND A.STDNT_ENRL_STATUS = 'E' AND C.EFFDT = ( SELECT MAX(C_ED.EFFDT) FROM %Table(CRSE_OFFER) C_ED WHERE C_ED.CRSE_ID = C.CRSE_ID AND C_ED.CRSE_OFFER_NBR = C.CRSE_OFFER_NBR AND C_ED.EFFDT <= S.SESS_BEGIN_DT)
226 POINTER
California Community Colleges Tech Center: Retrieves all the coursework for a given student and academic career.
0 HANDLE
